759
00:47:54,629 --> 00:47:56,060
Bagus.

760
00:47:56,060 --> 00:47:58,930
Akan butuh sekitar lima menit. Bobol brankas atau semacamnya.

761
00:47:59,029 --> 00:48:01,169
Brankasnya? Ide bagus.

762
00:48:11,449 --> 00:48:13,350
Katakan kode suara.

763
00:48:15,149 --> 00:48:17,719
