844
00:53:16,180 --> 00:53:17,319
- Teman-teman.
- Ini.

845
00:53:17,449 --> 00:53:18,489
Ada apa?

846
00:53:42,009 --> 00:53:44,140
Wajah yang menakutkan.

847
00:53:45,080 --> 00:53:46,949
Dengan video jelas ini,

848
00:53:47,080 --> 00:53:49,520
