851
00:53:57,960 --> 00:54:00,489
Dahulu dia anggota tim prajurit bayaran Rusia bernama Hantu.

852
00:54:00,930 --> 00:54:02,960
Mereka semua mati di atas kertas.

853
00:54:04,160 --> 00:54:05,469
